SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT DISTINCT A.CDNO AS ConstructionCode, A.Calculated_Value AS Qty,A.Material_Name AS BuzaiName, B.ConstructionCode,D.NameCode, C.SentProcessRequestDate AS KakouiraiSent, C.ProcessingRequestAcceptedDate AS KakouiraiCAD, C.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate AS ExpectedJoutou, C.ExpectedHouseRaisingDateAtRequested AS ShiyoushoJyoutou, G.AbbreviationName AS SEK_TYPE_NAME,E.SpecificationDetailName AS Syosai_Name, B.RequestWeek AS NP1Week,B.RequestYear AS NP1Year, B.RequestDestination AS NP1Destination FROM T_Cad_Data A
INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.ShipmentRequests B ON A.CDNO =B.CONSTRUCTIONCODE INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.ConstructionSchedule C ON A.CDNO = C.ConstructionCode INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.Constructions D ON A.CDNO = D.ConstructionCode INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.BasicSpecificationDetails E ON A.CDNO = E.ConstructionCode INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.Houses F ON A.CDNO = F.ConstructionCode INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HrdInformationService.dbo.ConstructionTypes G ON F.ConstructionTypeCode = G.ConstructionTypeCode
WHERE A.CDNO = ':1' AND B.ConstructionMaterialCode = 'NP' AND B.ConstructionMaterialDetailCode ='1' AND E.BasicSpecificationCode='0111' AND A.Material_Name = 'BD-4X19' AND A.Category_Type = 'NOKITEN KANAMONO(NP)'
